responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "70F211394093980FDD1CF8AD2E052DF4", "Yes. The Gravehide tribe has been a thorn in the side of my kin for a hundred years. To think we once commanded vermin like them, their very ancestors were my forebear\'s toys. Now they send curses and worse. I would overlook your presence in our range, if I knew killing Gravehide goblins to be your purpose. If you find evidence of their curses, I should like to see it.")
